<div class="tool-panel guide-panel">
  <div class="section-heading">
    <h2>怎么选参数</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="guide-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>声音原点</strong>
      <p>选一个声源作为时间基准，填入它到采集点的距离。工具以它为准对齐所有声源。</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <strong>声源距离</strong>
      <p>每个声源填它到同一采集点的直线距离。工具自动找出最晚到达的声源作为对齐基准。</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <strong>结果延迟</strong>
      <p>把每行计算出的延迟 (ms) 填入对应声源的 Delay 模块，即可使所有声源同时到达采集点。</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <strong>额外整体延迟</strong>
      <p>所有声源统一增加的延迟量，用于给后级处理器留 headroom。不影响声源间的相对同步。</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="tool-panel preset-panel">
  <div class="section-heading">
    <h2>场景预设</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="preset-row" aria-label="多点声源延时预设">
    <button type="button" data-multi-delay-preset="near-far">近远两点</button>
    <button type="button" data-multi-delay-preset="small-room">小房间</button>
    <button type="button" data-multi-delay-preset="with-headroom">带 1ms headroom</button>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="split-fields three">
  <div class="tool-panel compact-panel">
    <label class="field-label" for="sound-speed-input">声速 (m/s)</label>
    <input id="sound-speed-input" inputmode="decimal" value="343" readonly />
  </div>

  <div class="tool-panel compact-panel">
    <label class="toggle-field">
      <input id="temperature-mode-input" type="checkbox" />
      <span>按气温修正声速</span>
    </label>
    <label class="field-label" for="temperature-input">气温 (°C)</label>
    <input id="temperature-input" inputmode="decimal" value="20" disabled />
  </div>

  <div class="tool-panel compact-panel">
    <label class="field-label" for="extra-delay-input">额外整体延迟 (ms)</label>
    <input id="extra-delay-input" inputmode="decimal" value="0" />
  </div>
</div>

<div class="tool-panel compact-panel">
  <label class="field-label" for="origin-distance-input">声音原点到采集点距离 (m)</label>
  <input id="origin-distance-input" inputmode="decimal" value="3" />
</div>

<div class="split-fields">
  <div class="tool-panel compact-panel">
    <label class="field-label" for="origin-delay-input">原点推荐延迟 (ms)</label>
    <input id="origin-delay-input" inputmode="decimal" value="0" readonly />
  </div>

  <div class="tool-panel compact-panel">
    <label class="toggle-field">
      <input id="lock-origin-delay-input" type="checkbox" />
      <span>锁定原点延迟</span>
    </label>
    <label class="field-label" for="locked-origin-delay-input">锁定值 (ms)</label>
    <input id="locked-origin-delay-input" inputmode="decimal" value="0" disabled />
  </div>
</div>

<div class="tool-panel source-panel">
  <div class="section-heading">
    <h2>声源点</h2>
    <button class="ghost-button" type="button" data-source-add>增加</button>
  </div>
  <div class="source-header distance-header" aria-hidden="true">
    <span>名称</span>
    <span>到采集点距离 (m)</span>
    <span>传播时间 (ms)</span>
    <span>延迟 (ms)</span>
    <span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="source-list" data-source-list>
    <div class="source-row distance-row" data-source-row>
      <input data-source-name value="S1" aria-label="声源名称" placeholder="名称" />
      <input data-source-distance inputmode="decimal" value="2" aria-label="声源到采集点距离，单位 m" placeholder="距离 (m)" />
      <input data-source-travel readonly aria-label="声源传播时间，单位 ms" placeholder="自动计算" />
      <input data-source-delay readonly aria-label="声源延迟，单位 ms" placeholder="自动计算" />
      <button class="ghost-button icon-button" type="button" data-source-remove title="删除声源">
        <span aria-hidden="true">×</span>
        <span class="sr-only">删除声源</span>
      </button>
    </div>
    <div class="source-row distance-row" data-source-row>
      <input data-source-name value="S2" aria-label="声源名称" placeholder="名称" />
      <input data-source-distance inputmode="decimal" value="5" aria-label="声源到采集点距离，单位 m" placeholder="距离 (m)" />
      <input data-source-travel readonly aria-label="声源传播时间，单位 ms" placeholder="自动计算" />
      <input data-source-delay readonly aria-label="声源延迟，单位 ms" placeholder="自动计算" />
      <button class="ghost-button icon-button" type="button" data-source-remove title="删除声源">
        <span aria-hidden="true">×</span>
        <span class="sr-only">删除声源</span>
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="status-line" data-status data-state="ok">
  <span aria-hidden="true">●</span>
  <span>等待处理</span>
</div>

<div class="tool-panel result-panel">
  <div class="section-heading">
    <h2>结果抄写表</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="result-grid">
    <div class="result-row">
      <span>对齐基准</span>
      <strong data-multi-delay-result="anchor">-</strong>
      <em>自然最晚到达的点</em>
    </div>
    <div class="result-row">
      <span>目标到达时间</span>
      <strong data-multi-delay-result="target">-</strong>
      <em>所有声源最终对齐到这里</em>
    </div>
    <div class="result-row">
      <span>原点推荐延迟</span>
      <strong data-multi-delay-result="origin-delay">-</strong>
      <em>设置到声音原点</em>
    </div>
    <div class="result-row">
      <span>声速</span>
      <strong data-multi-delay-result="sound-speed">-</strong>
      <em>距离换算所用声速</em>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="tool-panel">
  <label class="field-label" for="multi-delay-output">输出</label>
  <textarea id="multi-delay-output" readonly spellcheck="false" placeholder="计算结果会显示在这里"></textarea>
</div>
